		"description": "Complete authentication API endpoints for Event Planning application using Laravel Sanctum.\n\n**Base URL:** http://eventplanning.test/api\n\n**How to use:**\n1. Import this file into Postman\n2. Run 'Register' or 'Login' - token will be auto-saved\n3. All protected endpoints will automatically use the saved token\n\n**Environment Variables (auto-managed):**\n- base_url: http://eventplanning.test/api\n- auth_token: (auto-saved after login/register)\n- user_id: (auto-saved)\n- user_email: (auto-saved)",
